description:
Part two of this week's show with the return of the insanely cool Allison Janney (Mom, The West Wing) is kicked off with a call to Sarah, who needs advice on whether or not she should break up with her boyfriend, and is topped off with a call to Katie, who’s unsure whether or not to take an internship that has a very unexpected twist!

Hosted on Acast. See acast.com/privacy for more information.
